name: Bargaining Table
Lore: 'The alcoves of Jabba''s palace are good places to make deals and place bets. Jabba gets a cut of the profits, of course.',
Text: 'Deploy on your side of table. Once per turn, you may cancel a Force drain by placing here from hand, one non-unique alien. Aliens may deploy from here as if from hand. (If effect canceled by opponent, any aliens here may immediately deploy for free).',
